// v1.5 forward: strict mode escalates a head-unresolved reference
// from `UnresolvedReference` (warning) to `UnknownReferenceType`
// (error). The head `mystery` isn't a known fn, sibling, or import.
// EXPECTED: ≥ 1 × UnknownReferenceType (name="mystery", path=["mystery"]).
#strict
{ x: mystery }
